## Summary of Restrictions

### What you CAN do:
- Use for learning and education
- Modify and study the code
- Share with other students
- Use in academic projects
- Research and experimentation

### What you CANNOT do:
- Use in commercial products
- Sell or license the software
- Use in safety-critical systems
- Claim as your own work
- Remove copyright notices

### Special Note for Universities:
This software is developed as part of university coursework at Tokaj-Hegyalja University. It is intended for academic use and should not be deployed in production environments or real-world security systems.
